records.name: Jen Maldives Male By Shangri-la

descriptions.direction: Located in Mal√©, JEN Maldives Male by Shangri-La is in the city center and near the beach. Maldives Islamic Centre and Medhu Ziyaaraiy are local landmarks, and some of the area's activities can be experienced at Hulhumale Ferry Terminal and Victory Wreck Dive Site.
descriptions.general: Located in the center of Maldives, JEN Maldives Male is right at the pulse of the city. From Valana International Airport, you can reach the hotel by speedboat in just a few minutes. Stroll the streets with ease and enjoy the urban Male or simply lounge by the rooftop infinity pool overlooking the stunning Indian Ocean.
